profile:
With 12 years of experience, we're a family owned and operated wildlife control company in the business of educating our clients and caring for the well being of the animals we handle.

Securing your home and safety while humanely capturing and relocating the unexpected guest is our top priority. Call us to schedule your inspection 905-617-0355.


Follow us on:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/K5Wildlife/
Instagram - @k5wildlife
services:
-Wildlife Removal of Birds, Bats, Mice, Raccoons, Rats, Skunks, Squirrels, Opossums and Snakes.
-24 hour Emergency services.
-Payment Plans Available. 
-Thorough inspections
-Locating/securing entry points.
-Property proofing
-Insulation Replacement
-Vent replacement and much more!

profile:
Raider Wildlife Control is a trusted pest removal service that uses humane methods to remove and prevent unwanted wildlife from entering your home or building. We focus on prevention to ensure that the problem is taken care of correctly the first time and you are not dealing with the same problem again in the future.

**Opening Hours**
Monday:          8:00am - 5:00pm

Wednesday:    8:00am - 5:00pm
